abstract: >-
  German-language clarification of the scientific, technical, evidence and
  patent-disclosure boundaries of the published QIK-VRT/EFFECT_ACK working
  paper, software snapshot and Internet-Draft. The status is
  PASS_WITH_EXPLICIT_BOUNDARIES; no universal totalization, physical-safety or
  patent guarantee is asserted.
